{"id":232699479,"title":"簡易聖誕半立體小卡片","content":"每年聖誕節我都會親手製作卡片給男友，今年也不例外。不過我的手工能力有限，只能做出一些簡單的半立體小卡片。\nhttps://megapx.dcard.tw/v1/images/e7b36668-d43f-412c-8141-b623ec3aa6d9/encode/1280\n卡片是用牛皮卡紙做的，外面包一層紅色紙，想要外觀比較簡潔，所以沒有太多裝飾，只用銀色油漆筆簡單畫一下，然後加個絲帶綁著。\nhttps://megapx.dcard.tw/v1/images/742ddc43-f621-4b5c-b3ab-461451bd79fb/encode/1280\n打開裡面是這樣的，這裡面貼了一張半透明的牛油紙（不是烹飪用的），有一棵半立體聖誕樹，上面貼了一些裝飾。白色部分是用油漆筆塗的，至於為什麼要畫我扔男友雪球，因為我喜歡欺負他🤣🤣\n祝福語我就碼掉了，太肉麻🙈\nhttps://megapx.dcard.tw/v1/images/48341e6d-430b-40c1-b86b-2a22fdbe4fd1/encode/1280\n放大聖誕樹部分，我自己是蠻喜歡這棵樹，覺得可愛。\n我是跟下面這個YouTube影片做的，真的很簡單，手殘的我也能做出來。\nhttps://youtu.be/zfLUb8KohpE","excerpt":"每年聖誕節我都會親手製作卡片給男友，今年也不例外。不過我的手工能力有限，只能做出一些簡單的半立體小卡片。卡片是用牛皮卡紙做的，外面包一層紅色紙，想要外觀比較簡潔，所以沒有太多裝飾，只用銀色油漆筆簡單畫","anonymousSchool":false,"anonymousDepartment":true,"pinned":false,"forumId":"c82dae3f-28ba-4aae-961d-c754e6ccd37a","replyId":null,"createdAt":"2019-12-16T16:03:00.414Z","updatedAt":"2019-12-16T16:03:00.414Z","commentCount":2,"likeCount":49,"tags":[],"topics":["卡片","插畫","手作","聖誕節","聖誕卡片"],"supportedReactions":null,"withNickname":false,"reportReason":"","hiddenByAuthor":false,"meta":{"layout":"classic"},"forumName":"手作","forumAlias":"handicrafts","school":"香港城市大學","replyTitle":null,"gender":"F","personaSubscriptable":null,"reactions":[{"id":"286f599c-f86a-4932-82f0-f5a06f1eca03","count":49}],"hidden":false,"customStyle":null,"isSuspiciousAccount":false,"layout":"classic","withImages":false,"withVideos":false,"media":[],"reportReasonText":"","mediaMeta":[{"id":"d8a6a070-d875-40b9-8855-7b517f5f2581","url":"https://megapx-assets.dcard.tw/images/e7b36668-d43f-412c-8141-b623ec3aa6d9/640.jpeg","normalizedUrl":"https://megapx-assets.dcard.tw/images/e7b36668-d43f-412c-8141-b623ec3aa6d9/640.jpeg","thumbnail":"https://megapx-assets.dcard.tw/images/e7b36668-d43f-412c-8141-b623ec3aa6d9/640.jpeg","type":"image/thumbnail","tags":[],"createdAt":"2019-12-16T16:03:00.414Z","updatedAt":"2019-12-16T16:03:00.414Z","width":480,"height":640},{"id":"d8a6a070-d875-40b9-8855-7b517